sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant API as Node.js Backend
    participant DB as MongoDB
    
    Client->>API: POST /api/auth/login (email, password)
    API->>DB: Verify credentials & password hash
    DB-->>API: Valid User
    
    API->>API: Generate RS256 Auth Token (15m)<br/>signed with AuthPrivate.pem
    API->>API: Generate RS256 Refresh Token (7d)<br/>signed with RefreshPrivate.pem
    
    API->>DB: Store Refresh Token hash in DB
    
    API->>Client: Set httpOnly cookies (Authentication, Refresh)
    
    note over Client,API: Subsequent Request
    Client->>API: GET /api/protected (sends cookies)
    API->>API: Verify Auth Token via AuthPublic.pem
    API-->>Client: 200 OK Response
    
    note over Client,API: Token Expiration Flow
    Client->>API: GET /api/protected (Auth Token Expired)
    API-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    
    Client->>API: POST /api/auth/refresh (sends Refresh cookie)
    API->>DB: Validate Refresh Token
    API->>API: Generate new Auth & Refresh Tokens
    API->>DB: Invalidate old Refresh Token, store new
    API->>Client: Set new httpOnly cookies
